# This file replaces .gitignore when building the pub archive, so it repeats the
# build and tooling excludes. Unanchored patterns match at any depth, covering
# example/ as well. These affect the published archive only.
.dart_tool/
build/
.fvm/
coverage/
staging/
*.log
.DS_Store
pubspec.lock
test/
dart_test.yaml
scripts/
lefthook.yml
CONTRIBUTING.md
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md

# Star-history chart, meaningful only on the GitHub README. Keeping it out trims
# ~108 KB from the archive.
assets/star-history/

# README hero imagery, resolved from the repository via relative links on
# pub.dev. Keeping it out trims ~650 KB. The pubspec screenshots (showcase,
# alert-button, switch-slider, select-checkbox) stay: pub.dev reads those from
# the archive.
assets/demo.gif
assets/logo.png

# Internal maintainer notes. doc/categories/ and dartdoc_options.yaml stay: they
# are dartdoc input. These are unreferenced prose that would otherwise ship unrendered.
doc/components/
doc/tools/
doc/package-size.md
